econd to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Sir William Lambourne was born in 1340, in Cornwall, England, his father, Sir William Lambourne, was 24 and his mother, Joanna Lansladrou, was 20. He married Joan Luscote. He died in 1375, in his hometown, at the age of 35."},"et":{"1340–1375":"1340–1375","1345–Female":"1345–Surnud","1344–1396":"1344–1396","1374–1431":"1374–1431","1317–Male":"1317–Surnud","1320–Female":"1320–Surnud","1345":"1345","1344":"1344","1431":"1431","Abt 1374":"umbes 1374","1375":"1375","1320":"1320","1374":"1374","1396":"1396","1340":"1340","1317":"1317","Lambourne, Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, England"},"fi":{"1340–1375":"1340–1375","1345–Female":"1345–Kuollut","1344–1396":"1344–1396","1374–1431":"1374–1431","1317–Male":"1317–Kuollut","1320–Female":"1320–Kuollut","1345":"1345","1344":"1344","1431":"1431","Abt 1374":"noin 1374","1375":"1375","1320":"1320","1374":"1374","1396":"1396","1340":"1340","1317":"1317","Lambourne, Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, England"},"fr":{"1340–1375":"1340–1375","1345–Female":"1345–Décédée","1344–1396":"1344–1396","1374–1431":"1374–1431","1317–Male":"1317–Décédé","1320–Female":"1320–Décédée","1345":"1345","1344":"1344","1431":"1431","Abt 1374":"environ 1374","1375":"1375","1320":"1320","1374":"1374","1396":"1396","1340":"1340","1317":"1317","Lambourne, Cornwall, England":"Cornouailles, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Sir William Lambourne est né en 1340, à Cornouailles, Angleterre, son père, Sir William Lambourne, avait 24 ans et sa mère, Joanna Lansladrou, avait 20 ans. Il a épousé Joan Luscote. Il est décédé en 1375, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 35 ans."},"de":{"1340–1375":"1340–1375","1345–Female":"1345–Verstorben","1344–1396":"1344–1396","1374–1431":"1374–1431","1317–Male":"1317–Verstorben","1320–Female":"1320–Verstorben","1345":"1345","1344":"1344","1431":"1431","Abt 1374":"um 1374","1375":"1375","1320":"1320","1374":"1374","1396